      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait really?? i mean it's mostly just kinda a dull ache and i feel a bit nauseous but it feels so much like the time i had bad indigestion last month. i dont want to go to the er and pay like $1000 just for heartburn lol. are you sure it's not just the pizza? can i just try an antacid first and see if it gets better in 20 mins?",
