    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear you but i'm literally just sitting here on the couch and i don't feel like i'm dying or anything. it's just a weird discomfort. honestly if i call 911 they'll just think im being dramatic. can you just tell me if there's any way to tell for sure if it's just gas? like are there other signs i should look for that would prove its definitely just indigestion?",
